<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/jonathan-reynolds> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Jonathan Reynolds was appointed Parliamentary Secretary to the Treasury (Chief Whip) on 5 September 2025. He was previously Secretary of State for Business and Trade and President of the Board of Trade from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Stalybridge and Hyde in May 2010."@en .
